Prayer,Planet,is,an,online,community,of,people,worldwide,who,commit,to,praying,for,each,other,s,prayer,lists,Users,can,create,and,share,their,prayer,lists,with,the,Prayer,Planet,community,for,constant,prayer,Users,can,access,Prayer,Planet,via,mobile,devices,IM,and,on,the,web,The,Prayer,Planet,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,the,most,recent,messages,on,Prayer,Planet,access,direct,messages,retrieve,user,information,and,add,friends,from,Prayer,Planet